Ayo, Mrinu.  Mari ikut saya.

00:29:40.240 --> 00:29:41.360
Kamu tinggal.

00:29:45.080 --> 00:29:46.400
Dia hanya..

00:29:50.080 --> 00:29:51.960
Kenapa kamu
menatapku seperti itu?

